Like what is the happiest thing in your life?

87
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:14,120
Well,

88
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:16,360
maybe...

89
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:19,320
spending time together with you.

90
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,120
That's touching, huh?

91
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:31,560
So, when I went to the toilet,

92
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:33,280
did anyone ask your number?

93
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:34,920
Nope,

94
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,840
