-Really?

95
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,320
I don't even have a phone.

96
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:41,960
Right.

97
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,640
You don't have a phone.

98
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:49,200
