99
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,520
not even on social media.

100
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,040
Don't you feel alone?

101
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,320
I'm scared to use it.

102
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,360
I'm afraid.

103
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:03,320
Since I got sick,

104
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,400
my world's shrunk a lot.

105
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:10,000
I didn't get to play outside like other kids.

106
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,760
Didn't go to school.

107
00:08:13,520 --> 00:08:16,080
My life was just home and hospital.

108
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:20,360
When I go out,

109
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:24,120
it's always with family.

110
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:27,760
But it's not too bad, you know.

111
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,640
I'm happy in my little world.

112
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,320
But without them,

113
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,559
