116
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:51,560
I don't know how I'd feel about that.

117
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:08,280
Hey, it's alright.

118
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:10,640
I'll show you the world myself.

119
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,120
Alright?

120
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,240
But for tonight,

121
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,120
