122
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:19,880
It's getting late now.

123
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,880
So, want me to drop you?

124
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,960
No worries,

125
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:27,640
-I'll take a taxi.
-Sure?

126
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:30,680
-You've got work tomorrow, right?
-Yep.

127
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,000
Then...

128
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:35,360
-Shall we ask for the bill?
-Okay.

129
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:38,800
Excuse me, can we get the bill?

130
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,920
-I'll pay for it.
-Oh, no need.

131
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,240
I've got this one.

132
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:46,200
You paid me for the whole day, let me pay it.

133
00:09:46,880 --> 00:09:48,080
I'll treat you.

134
00:09:48,800 --> 00:09:50,880
Save your money for the cab. I've got it.

135
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,320
Pond, stop it! I'm not playing.

136
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:03,160
I mean it, I'll actually do it.

137
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,880
You're not ready for this, trust me.

138
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:08,200
