146
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,640
Oops!

147
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:25,040
Sorry!

148
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:27,560
Hello, here for a haircut?

149
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:29,440
Yes.

150
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:31,800
-Welcome.
-Right this way.

151
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:34,040
-Please follow me.
-Don't be scared.

152
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:41,600
-Take a seat here.
-Please, sit down.

153
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:47,000
Just keep your hair clipper.

154
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,800
Man, you're always eager to cut hair!

155
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,760
Sorry for the mess.

156
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:58,800
I'm practicing haircutting.

157
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:00,960
No worries.

158
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:03,560
Well, it looks fun.

159
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,120
No, it's not fun.

160
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,960
We're just kids at heart.

161
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,280
What haircut do you want?

162
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,480
Skinhead?

163
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,200
Skinhead?

164
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:20,960
I have cancer.

165
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:25,040
My hair's falling out from chemo.

166
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:28,000
Thought I'd just shave it all off.

167
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:31,400
Less distracting.

168
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,400
Sorry to hear that.

169
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:39,480
Hope you get better soon.

170
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:46,320
My dad died of cancer too.

171
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:54,200
Still don't get why I keep treating it.

172
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:59,320
Maybe, I do it for those behind me.

173
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:07,440
Treatment just adds a little time.

174
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,760
But I think that little time is meaningful.

175
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:17,720
Even a little time can create a lot.

176
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:20,360
Create some good memories.

177
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:26,040
But eventually we will forget about them,

178
00:12:28,400 --> 00:12:30,320
no matter how many good memories,

179
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:33,880
It´s true.

180
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:41,280
But those who remain still remember.

181
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,480
Sorry,

182
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,280
I talked too much.

183
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:51,280
No worries.

184
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:56,000
Thank you.

185
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:03,520
Sorry about that.

186
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,800
Got a bit hectic earlier.

187
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:09,200
What haircut would you like, sir?

188
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,520
Skinhead, please.

189
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:13,560
Uh...

190
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:16,360
Can he shave my head?

191
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,640
