-You sure?

192
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:23,680
It's just shaving.

193
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:26,200
He won't cut off my head, I guess.

194
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:29,160
Let him do it, please.

195
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,480
Alright then.

196
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:33,840
Take care of it, okay?

197
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:38,960
I'll do my best.

198
00:13:55,040 --> 00:13:55,960
Ready?

199
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:31,120
