200
00:14:33,880 --> 00:14:36,520
Great, you've got a gentle touch, bro.

201
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,800
Thank you so much.

202
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,680
How much's this?

203
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:43,720
No charge for this one.

204
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:47,360
Consider it a lesson for Pond to practice.

205
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,000
Thanks again.

206
00:14:52,400 --> 00:14:53,760
Pond&Mac: Thank you.

207
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,440
Thank you.

208
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:07,840
You're lucky today.

209
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:10,440
Tomorrow, your head's my practice canvas.

210
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,760
You just zip it!

211
00:15:13,040 --> 00:15:15,840
-You'd better do here.
-What?

212
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:19,600
Here it is.

213
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:21,720
This is your job.

214
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:23,320
Here's the broom.

215
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:25,360
Get sweeping!

216
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:31,360
