218
00:16:10,160 --> 00:16:11,920
Pond!

219
00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:17,080
Vin!

220
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:21,120
Watch out, Vin!

221
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:25,760
Vin...!

222
00:16:27,920 --> 00:16:32,320
Lift your head and breathe...

223
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:35,320
Feeling better now?

224
00:16:55,400 --> 00:16:56,720
Vin!

225
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,400
Come here!

226
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:04,640
Let's eat, so you can take your pill.

227
00:17:21,520 --> 00:17:23,599
Careful, it's hot.

228
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:24,920
Blow it first.

229
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:28,240
-Let me help.
-No, I'm good.

230
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:31,080
I can handle it myself.

231
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:37,080
Not gonna blow?

232
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:39,880
Here...

233
00:17:41,600 --> 00:17:44,000
I have an old phone for you.

234
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:50,920
Why give this to me?

235
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:53,480
It's weird not having a phone.

236
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:56,160
I wouldn't call anyone, though.

237
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,080
Then call me,

238
00:17:59,360 --> 00:18:00,800
or I can call you too.

239
00:18:02,760 --> 00:18:06,840
What, gonna wish me good morning and good night?

240
00:18:08,080 --> 00:18:11,320
Sure, I can do that. No sweat.

241
00:18:13,040 --> 00:18:15,160
But mainly, it's for when you're sick,

242
00:18:15,720 --> 00:18:18,200
Like today. Imagine if I hadn't arrived on time.

243
00:18:18,600 --> 00:18:20,040
Shouldn't you have gone to the afterlife?

244
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:22,760
I did want to go soon.

245
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:25,280
Life's exhausting.

246
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:27,280
Hit your mouth three thousand times.

247
00:18:27,920 --> 00:18:29,080
Just joking!

248
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:31,680
Why the hurry? You've got more photos to take.

249
00:18:33,440 --> 00:18:35,680
-I said I was kidding.
-Gosh!

250
00:18:41,760 --> 00:18:42,760
Here, do this.

251
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:45,440
I'll set up Instagram for you.

252
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:50,360
On Instagram

253
00:18:51,160 --> 00:18:54,160
