259
00:19:21,320 --> 00:19:22,280
Okay.

260
00:19:26,280 --> 00:19:27,840
You know how it works?

261
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,000
Hey Vin.

262
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:38,080
