270
00:20:04,760 --> 00:20:06,960
-Delete it.
-No, it's my phone.

271
00:20:07,440 --> 00:20:09,280
-My choice.
-These photos are too dark.

272
00:20:10,120 --> 00:20:11,040
Delete that!

273
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:12,680
My decision, dude.

274
00:20:14,520 --> 00:20:15,680
-Just delete it.
-Hey...

275
00:20:16,240 --> 00:20:17,320
So, don't post it okay?

276
00:20:18,040 --> 00:20:19,160
-Please!
-Okay.

277
00:20:19,520 --> 00:20:20,640
