00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:23,520
It's awful. You're not great at this, huh?

279
00:20:27,280 --> 00:20:29,160
Alright, all set, sir.

280
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:30,640
Excuse me...

281
00:20:32,520 --> 00:20:35,200
-How much?
-120 baht, sir.

282
00:20:42,120 --> 00:20:43,880
-Thanks.
-Thank you.

283
00:20:54,920 --> 00:20:55,920
Hello!

284
00:20:56,920 --> 00:20:57,800
Vin!

285
00:20:58,520 --> 00:20:59,600
What brings you here?

286
00:21:00,640 --> 00:21:04,200
Just wanted to see your workplace.

287
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:07,880
Pond, you know this guy?

288
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:10,680
That's Marvin, my ghost buddy.

289
00:21:11,280 --> 00:21:13,560
Oh, this guy. Nice to meet you.

290
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,160
I'm Mac.

291
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:17,360
Need a haircut?

292
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:19,920
Trying to make a quick buck, eh?

293
00:21:20,640 --> 00:21:21,920
-Absolutely!
- I'd love to.

294
00:21:22,320 --> 00:21:24,360
But I just got trimmed.

295
00:21:26,040 --> 00:21:27,640
How about a hair wash?

296
00:21:28,520 --> 00:21:30,920
Just washed it before coming.

297
00:21:31,200 --> 00:21:32,160
Oh!

298
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:35,200
Where to next?

299
00:21:35,360 --> 00:21:37,640
Pond can take care of you.

300
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:40,800
Um...

301
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:43,000
sounds good.

302
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:45,400
-Alright!
-Pond, your turn.

303
00:21:46,560 --> 00:21:48,200
-Take care of him.
-Got it.

304
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:58,720
How do you want it styled?

305
00:22:00,800 --> 00:22:02,000
I don't know, bro.

306
00:22:02,520 --> 00:22:04,080
Never really styled it before.

307
00:22:06,120 --> 00:22:07,680
Set it how you think is handsome.

308
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:11,400
Okay, but my idea of 'handsome' might be different.

309
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:13,160
Just go for it.

310
00:22:13,760 --> 00:22:17,080
-I'm the customer here.
-Okay, dude.

311
00:23:14,840 --> 00:23:15,680
How's it?

312
00:23:17,040 --> 00:23:17,880
Like it?

313
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:21,120
Hmm,

314
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:23,760
super handsome.

315
00:23:24,720 --> 00:23:28,120
- Bro, you've made so many dreams come true,
- It's nothing.

316
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:31,440
You know, you could style it yourself at home.

317
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:32,680
No,

318
00:23:33,520 --> 00:23:38,640
I dreamed that if you had a shop, I'd like to be your customer.

319
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:46,960
Then, if you like, shall we take a picture together?

320
00:23:48,080 --> 00:23:49,240
-Mac!
-Sup!

321
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:51,320
-Snap a picture for us?
-Sure thing, one sec.

322
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:52,600
Just use your phone.

323
00:23:54,520 --> 00:23:56,400
Alright, come on.

324
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:03,280
Okay, come on.

325
00:24:03,760 --> 00:24:04,800
Ready?

326
00:24:06,560 --> 00:24:09,160
1...2...3

327
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:10,400
One more.

328
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:12,560
-Just smile, man.
-Okay, smiling.

329
00:24:13,720 --> 00:24:14,480
Cheese!

330
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:17,120
1, 2,  cheese!

331
00:24:17,560 --> 00:24:19,840
Awesome, that's a great shot!

332
00:24:20,080 --> 00:24:21,400
-Let's see.
-Check it out.

333
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:23,640
Here...

334
00:24:26,240 --> 00:24:27,200
Where you would like to go next?

335
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:30,560
We're pretty lucky today.

336
00:24:31,280 --> 00:24:33,000
Usually there are a lot of people in this place.

337
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:37,520
Pond, you come here often?

338
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:40,880
Yeah, but I usually skip it because of the queue.

339
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:44,160
Hey!

340
00:24:45,520 --> 00:24:47,480
-What a coincidence!
-Oh, Mr. Barber.

341
00:24:48,320 --> 00:24:49,520
Here for a meal?

342
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:51,080
Yeah,

343
00:24:51,560 --> 00:24:53,920
-I'm here with my girlfriend.
-Got a table yet?

344
00:24:55,520 --> 00:24:57,200
Still waiting in line.

345
00:24:58,800 --> 00:24:59,960
Join us, won't you?

346
00:25:00,520 --> 00:25:03,120
More people, more fun. And you don't have to wait.

347
00:25:05,200 --> 00:25:06,040
Come on!

348
00:25:07,080 --> 00:25:07,760
Yes, sure.

349
00:25:11,960 --> 00:25:12,960
How often do you come here?

350
00:25:13,400 --> 00:25:14,880
Sometimes...

351
00:25:15,360 --> 00:25:17,880
-Long wait normally, right?
-Yeah, it's pretty long.

352
00:25:18,840 --> 00:25:21,480
By the way, I still don't know your name.

353
00:25:22,040 --> 00:25:23,840
I'm Pond, and this is Marvin.

354
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:27,160
Shin here and...

355
00:25:28,600 --> 00:25:29,520
Meaw, my girlfriend.

356
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,480
Nice to meet you all.

357
00:25:34,480 --> 00:25:37,360
Meaw and I met back in university.

358
00:25:37,800 --> 00:25:39,760
Started like a sister,

359
00:25:40,600 --> 00:25:43,200
now she's my world.

360
00:25:43,800 --> 00:25:45,280
Whoa!

361
00:25:46,400 --> 00:25:47,840
How envious!

362
00:25:48,440 --> 00:25:49,960
It's obvious,

363
00:25:50,600 --> 00:25:52,640
I envy myself too.

364
00:25:53,600 --> 00:25:56,560
If not her, then who else?

365
00:25:59,800 --> 00:26:02,120
You're being cheesy, huh?

366
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:03,840
Not at all.

367
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:06,880
Well, I'm off to the toilet now.

368
00:26:07,840 --> 00:26:09,200
Keep the praise down a bit, okay?

369
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,720
Okay.

370
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:17,880
She's so cute, really.

371
00:26:19,760 --> 00:26:21,000
Hey, bro!

372
00:26:22,560 --> 00:26:24,400
Remember that chat we had earlier?

373
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:25,880
Yes.

374
00:26:28,120 --> 00:26:29,080
At first,

375
00:26:30,240 --> 00:26:36,200
I didn't quite get why you said those things so sincerely

376
00:26:37,640 --> 00:26:39,000
until I heard about Marvin.

377
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:46,320
What were you guys talking about before?

378
00:26:53,320 --> 00:26:54,440
Marvin,

379
00:26:57,640 --> 00:27:00,000
our lives might not be long,

380
00:27:05,280 --> 00:27:06,880
but having someone special

381
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:10,280
can truly make you the happiest.

382
00:27:12,720 --> 00:27:13,400
So,

383
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:16,360
you guys, be my witnesses.

384
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:18,760
Witnesses?

385
00:27:27,080 --> 00:27:28,360
Meaw,

386
00:27:58,080 --> 00:27:59,360
I'm sorry

387
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:06,000
for the tough times ahead.

388
00:28:08,760 --> 00:28:10,400
And thank you

389
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:16,840
for filling my life with meaning.

390
00:28:22,720 --> 00:28:25,280
Thank you for being the joy in my life.

391
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:32,280
I don't know...

392
00:28:34,120 --> 00:28:38,160
what the future holds,

393
00:28:43,200 --> 00:28:44,560
but from now on,

394
00:28:49,800 --> 00:28:51,720
I want to be by your side forever.

395
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:04,040
Will you marry me?

396
00:29:14,760 --> 00:29:16,160
Yes, I will.

397
00:29:41,960 --> 00:29:43,240
Congratulations!

398
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:45,080
Thank you.

399
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:51,280
Want it?

400
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:53,280
Already?

401
00:29:56,760 --> 00:29:59,120
-It's done already.
-Yeah... it's done.

402
00:30:02,560 --> 00:30:04,240
-It's great, isn't it?
-Huh?

403
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:08,440
Shin must be so happy to be with someone he loves.

404
00:30:09,480 --> 00:30:10,600
Hmm,

405
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:14,560
the best life is probably one filled with happiness.

406
00:30:21,280 --> 00:30:22,960
Thank you so much, bro,

407
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:26,360
for making me the happiest I've been in years.

408
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,960
Ever since my family left,

409
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:34,120
it's been lonely and tough.

410
00:30:36,080 --> 00:30:39,200
I'm scared of feeling that way again.

411
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:44,800
If I have to be alone again someday,

412
00:30:47,320 --> 00:30:49,720
I'd rather die while I'm happy like this.

413
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:51,520
Have you gone mad?

414
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:54,320
I'm here with you, aren't I?

415
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:57,320
Crazy, Pond!

416
00:30:58,560 --> 00:31:00,160
You have your own life.

417
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:03,000
One day...

418
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:05,440
you'll find someone you love,

419
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:09,120
get married,

420
00:31:11,040 --> 00:31:12,600
and I won't be there.

421
00:31:14,400 --> 00:31:15,880
Don't think like that.

422
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:18,720
I love you, man.

423
00:31:19,920 --> 00:31:20,920
I'll be with you,

424
00:31:21,760 --> 00:31:23,040
stay with you forever.

425
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:27,520
Really?

426
00:31:30,040 --> 00:31:32,400
-You won't leave me, really?
-Really.

427
00:31:33,320 --> 00:31:34,200
I won't leave.

428
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:36,320
I'll make you happy.

429
00:31:38,120 --> 00:31:39,720
Wherever you want to go, eat or do,

430
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:42,000
I'll be there with you.

431
00:31:43,280 --> 00:31:45,520
We'll create memories together.

432
00:31:46,760 --> 00:31:47,760
you and me.

433
00:31:49,320 --> 00:31:51,720
Let's make life happy together.

434
00:31:54,360 --> 00:31:56,320
Um.

435
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:02,360
Then...

436
00:32:05,080 --> 00:32:06,840
Can you help me set up the tent, bro?

437
00:32:10,480 --> 00:32:11,240
Over there?

438
00:32:12,600 --> 00:32:13,240
Yes.

439
00:32:14,360 --> 00:32:16,640
-Felt like camping today.
-Really?

440
00:32:19,720 --> 00:32:24,000
Thought a sudden trip elsewhere might be too much.

441
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:27,920
Hey, no need to be so considerate. Just tell me
where you want to go.

442
00:32:30,560 --> 00:32:31,240
Okay,

443
00:32:32,040 --> 00:32:33,160
you just said it.

444
00:32:34,160 --> 00:32:37,600
But let's camp with me right here for now.

445
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:43,920
Cool, you handle the BBQ, I'll get the tent.

446
00:32:45,320 --> 00:32:46,760
-Deal!
-Let's go.

447
00:33:02,160 --> 00:33:04,760
I'm really happy, you know.

448
00:33:08,280 --> 00:33:10,240
Even this backyard camping is so fun.

449
00:33:12,040 --> 00:33:14,680
Imagine how fun it would be a mountain trip together.

450
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:19,200
Next time, let's go to Khao Yai.

451
00:33:20,360 --> 00:33:21,520
Drive around,

452
00:33:21,840 --> 00:33:23,960
camp out, splash in waterfalls.

453
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:28,800
Inviting others could be even more fun.

454
00:33:31,560 --> 00:33:33,080
Yeah, just the thought of it is exciting.

455
00:33:34,800 --> 00:33:35,600
But...

456
00:33:36,840 --> 00:33:38,960
will others be keen to come?

457
00:33:40,560 --> 00:33:41,240
Of course,

458
00:33:42,800 --> 00:33:45,960
Last time was just a plan change, no worries.

459
00:33:47,720 --> 00:33:49,160
This time, we don't have to invite everyone.

460
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:51,360
Only the well-known ones.

461
00:33:52,560 --> 00:33:53,360
I'll drag Mac along too.

462
00:33:55,320 --> 00:33:59,040
Yeah, that could work, bro.

463
00:34:10,560 --> 00:34:12,360
Hey, bro...

464
00:34:15,679 --> 00:34:16,679
thanks...

465
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:19,960
for living the dream with me.

466
00:34:22,920 --> 00:34:23,920
It's okay.

467
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:25,480
I already told you, right?

468
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:27,800
I'll do my best.

469
00:34:39,040 --> 00:34:40,440
Just one regret though

470
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:45,080
There's one thing you can't do for me for sure.

471
00:34:47,239 --> 00:34:48,120
What's that?

472
00:34:51,040 --> 00:34:52,480
Graduation photos...

473
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:56,639
I wanted to take them with everyone.

474
00:35:02,600 --> 00:35:05,960
Got this huge frame at home for it.

475
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:13,360
Actually, I wanted it to hold my graduation photo.

476
00:35:16,560 --> 00:35:17,880
But I know...

477
00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:21,120
can't rewind time to take it.

478
00:35:24,240 --> 00:35:25,680
My parents are gone too.

479
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:28,880
Some moments...

480
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:31,520
if we missed once,

481
00:35:33,680 --> 00:35:35,480
we are lost them forever.

482
00:35:38,320 --> 00:35:40,320
That's why we have to make every day count.

483
00:35:44,720 --> 00:35:48,680
What's past may need to be let go.

484
00:35:52,080 --> 00:35:53,000
But from now on,

485
00:35:54,600 --> 00:35:55,840
and in days ahead...

486
00:36:00,040 --> 00:36:02,800
let's fill them with happiness together.

487
00:36:07,080 --> 00:36:07,760
Um...

488
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:14,240
really, thanks, bro.

489
00:36:16,600 --> 00:36:17,720
I'm glad

490
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:21,560
you're here with me today.

491
00:38:22,960 --> 00:38:23,680
Vin!

492
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:32,320
Oh, Vin!

493
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:35,960
Vin!

494
00:38:46,280 --> 00:38:47,160
Vin!

495
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:52,240
Vin...!

496
00:38:52,720 --> 00:38:55,640
Vin, wake up!

497
00:38:58,840 --> 00:39:00,360
Somebody help...

498
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:03,280
Vin...!

499
00:39:03,640 --> 00:39:04,360
Damn it!

500
00:39:06,800 --> 00:39:07,960
Vin...!

501
00:39:13,000 --> 00:39:15,160
Somebody, help!

502
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:18,000
Vin, the doctor's coming.

503
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:21,280
What's gonna happen to him?

504
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:23,520
His condition is still critical.

505
00:39:23,840 --> 00:39:24,960
We need to keep a close watch.

506
00:39:25,680 --> 00:39:28,720
Can't say for sure yet.

507
00:39:29,360 --> 00:39:30,760
You might have to prepare for the worst.

508
00:39:31,400 --> 00:39:33,560
We'll go on a trip together, remember?

509
00:39:34,640 --> 00:39:35,840
Vin!

510
00:39:36,320 --> 00:39:37,920
Do something, doctor!

511
00:39:38,200 --> 00:39:39,880
Vin, wake up, man.

512
00:39:41,560 --> 00:39:42,360
Hey!

513
00:39:42,720 --> 00:39:43,520
Damn mirror!

514
00:39:44,680 --> 00:39:46,040
If you're really magic,

515
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:51,240
can't you make Marvin's wish come true?

516
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:55,800
Or If you can't rewind time,

517
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:59,160
at least wake Marvin up.

518
00:40:06,520 --> 00:40:11,960
Didn't you bring me here just to make Marvin happy?

519
00:40:15,240 --> 00:40:16,560
If you're really powerful,

520
00:40:17,560 --> 00:40:20,080
show me a miracle, please!

521
00:40:27,480 --> 00:40:29,640
Don't you want Marvin to be happy?

522
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:34,800
If you really want me to help Marvin, then help me too.

523
00:40:35,640 --> 00:40:39,240
Let me fulfill Marvin's dream at once.

524
00:40:40,040 --> 00:40:42,640
I'm begging you, for fuck's sake.

525
00:41:38,440 --> 00:41:39,440
Hey Pond,

526
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:41,440
you lost in thought?

527
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:45,280
Pond, photo time!

528
00:41:47,400 --> 00:41:48,560
Come on over.

529
00:41:49,560 --> 00:41:50,920
Let's take photos with us.

530
00:41:52,200 --> 00:41:54,160
Come on, stand in the middle.

531
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:56,240
Look at the camera.

532
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:58,840
Look over there!

533
00:42:02,160 --> 00:42:03,560
Smile big, bro!

534
00:42:05,800 --> 00:42:07,320
Smile!

535
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:11,360
Where's Marvin...?

536
00:42:11,920 --> 00:42:13,160
Vin's not here today.

537
00:42:13,320 --> 00:42:14,280
Why?

538
00:42:14,480 --> 00:42:16,840
His uncle said he's sick.

539
00:42:18,120 --> 00:42:18,840
Right?

540
00:42:19,640 --> 00:42:20,360
Let´s do this.

541
00:42:21,320 --> 00:42:24,360
Wait up, don't go anywhere. Hold off starting without me, alright? I'll be right back.

542
00:42:24,720 --> 00:42:25,600
Oh, wait!

543
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:26,400
Where are you going?

544
00:42:26,760 --> 00:42:28,200
Gonna get Marvin for the picture. Don't start yet!

545
00:42:28,520 --> 00:42:29,400
Oh...

546
00:42:29,840 --> 00:42:31,080
Hold up, man!

547
00:42:31,240 --> 00:42:32,200
Why's he stalling us?

548
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:35,520
Marvin!

549
00:42:36,200 --> 00:42:37,120
Marvin!

550
00:42:38,120 --> 00:42:39,600
Marvin...!

551
00:42:49,560 --> 00:42:50,280
Pond!

552
00:42:51,920 --> 00:42:52,640
Hold on, young man.

553
00:42:53,920 --> 00:42:55,000
What are you doing here?

554
00:42:56,400 --> 00:42:58,560
Gonna take Marvin to graduation pics.

555
00:42:59,880 --> 00:43:01,440
With our tutor gang.

556
00:43:02,440 --> 00:43:05,880
Um, Marvin is still sick, he can't go.

557
00:43:06,960 --> 00:43:08,000
But if not now,

558
00:43:08,800 --> 00:43:10,160
they'll never happen again.

559
00:43:11,760 --> 00:43:13,680
It happens only once, Marvin.

560
00:43:14,240 --> 00:43:16,960
I said no, he's unwell.

561
00:43:17,400 --> 00:43:19,160
